diff.printer_settings_id: Creality Ender-3 S1 Pro (0.3 mm nozzle) - Custom
diff.start_gcode:
; 
; Custom START G-Code BEGIN
;

G90 ; use absolute coordinates
M83 ; extruder relative mode
M104 S150 ; set temporary nozzle temp to prevent oozing during homing
M140 S{first_layer_bed_temperature[0]} ; set final bed temp
G4 S30 ; allow partial nozzle warmup
G28 ; home all axis and restore leveling

; Original START_GCODE values
;G1 Z50 F240
;G1 X2.0 Y10 F3000
;M104 S{first_layer_temperature[0]} ; set final nozzle temp
;M190 S{first_layer_bed_temperature[0]} ; wait for bed temp to stabilize
;M109 S{first_layer_temperature[0]} ; wait for nozzle temp to stabilize
;G1 Z0.28 F240
;G92 E0
;G1 X2.0 Y140 E10 F1500     ; prime the nozzle
;G1 X2.3 Y140 F5000
;G92 E0
;G1 X2.3 Y10 E10 F1200      ; prime the nozzle
;G92 E0

; Modified G-code (sets the extruder off the edge of the bed for the
; nozzle warm up, and draws more prime lines)

G1 F3000 Z5                 ; Move Z Axis up a bit during heating to not damage bed
G1 F5000 X-4.2 Y20          ; Move the extruder to the far left of the plate before heating
G1 F5000 Z0.1               ; Lower the extruder so that the tip is at the same level as the bed, so the filament can be cut off 

M104 S{first_layer_temperature[0]}      ; set final nozzle temp
M190 S{first_layer_bed_temperature[0]}  ; wait for bed temp to stabilize
M109 S{first_layer_temperature[0]}      ; wait for nozzle temp to stabilize

G1 F1500 X2                 ; This should cut off any filament that dropped out during heating
G1 F1500 Z5 Y20             ; Move to the start position
G1 F5000 Z{layer_height}    ; Drop the Z axis for drawing the first line
G92 E0

G1 F1500 Y200 E8            ; Draw the first line
G1 F5000 X2.5               ; Move to side a little

G92 E0

G1 F1500 Y20 E8             ; Draw the second line
G1 F5000 X3                 ; Move to side a little
G92 E0

G1 F1500 Y200 E8            ; Draw the third line
G1 F5000 X3.5               ; Move to side a little
G92 E0

G1 F1500 Y20 E8             ; Draw the fourth (and final) line

G1 F3000 Z3                 ; Move Z Axis up little to prevent scratching of Heat Bed
G1 F5000 X5 Z{layer_height} ; Move over to prevent blob squish
G92 E0

; 
; Custom START G-Code END
;
